    <story>
        <scene id="0" background="bg.jpg">
            <bgm src="mid-lude.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <cg src="lastChapter.png" bg="bg.jpg"></cg>
            <goto goto="10" change="#000000"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="10" background="blackHole.jpg">
            <bgm src="03_15_ruinBerlin.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <text>奥托·阿波卡利斯眼中的世界扭曲了。</text>
            <text>他察觉到万物正在自己的眼前瓦解。</text>
            <text>他察觉到时间正在被扔进一个巨大的搅拌机里。</text>
            <text>过去、现在、未来，一切都在无穷无尽的减速与断片中，变得模糊不清。</text>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">黑洞。</p>
                <p class="article-text">他从爱因斯坦的论文里读到过这个物理学概念。</p>
                <p class="article-text">大多数情况下，它们是质量超过太阳三倍的恒星内核，在核聚变的燃料耗尽后发生引力坍缩的结果。</p>
            </text>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">这些星体内部的引力是如此之大，以至于没有任何微观结构能够阻止它们继续向更小的体积垮塌。</p>
                <br />
                <p class="article-text">……所以，最终的结果只会如此：那重达数百万个地球的庞然大物，自我压缩成了一个只具有质量、电荷、角动量的——点。</p>
            </text>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">在这个点的周围，它产生的引力场是如此之强，以至于任何辐射都不能从其内部逃脱；</p>
                <br />
                <p class="article-text">而在外界看来，任何落入它周遭无法观测区域的过程，也都将消耗无穷长的时间。</p>
            </text>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">在这个被称作“视界”的区域之前，一切有限的过程，都将延展至无穷。</p>
            </text>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">特别地，对于正从外部悄悄接收着终端信号的他而言——</p>
                <br />
                <p class="article-text">意识，正逐渐被撕裂。</p>
            </text>
            <goto goto="20" change="#000000"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="20" background="dreamSky.jpg">
            <bgm src="11_17_memory.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <show chara="kallenChristMemoryFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">“所谓人生，不过是一个行走的影子、”</speak>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">“一个在舞台上指手划脚的拙劣伶人——”</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristMercyFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">“登场片刻，就在无声无息中悄然退下；”</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristDeterminedFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">“它是一个愚者所讲的故事，充满着喧哗和骚动，”</speak>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">“却找不到一点儿意义。”</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">……</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">你、你、你……</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">我、我、我……</speak>
            <bgm src="horror.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <show chara="kallenChristMercyFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">奥托·阿波卡利斯。</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristDeterminedFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">“他将要藐视命运，唾弃死生，”</speak>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">“超越一切的情理，排除一切的疑虑，”</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristMercyFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">“执着于他的不可能的希望。” </speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">不、不对……</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">你……</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">你不是……</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristMemoryFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">“以不义开始的事情，必须用罪恶使它巩固。”</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristDeterminedFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">从一开始，这就是一条死路——</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristMercyFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">——我的奥托·阿波卡利斯啊。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">……你倒底是谁！</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristDeterminedFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">你害怕这样的话题，奥托·阿波卡利斯。</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristMemoryFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">“我已经两足深陷于血泊之中，要是不再涉血前进，那么回头的路也是同样使人厌倦的。”</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristMercyFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">可是……到头来，你其实什么也改变不了。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">不！不对！</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">一切都在按照我的计划发展！</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristDeterminedFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">……你的计划？</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristMercyFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">你从来就没有计划。</speak>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">你只会停留在过去的命运里自怨自艾；</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristMemoryFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">“而命运也像娼妓一样，有意向这个叛徒卖弄风情，助长他的罪恶的气焰。”</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">我——</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">我的卡莲才不会这样说话！</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristDeterminedFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">但是你自己会，奥托·阿波卡利斯先生。</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristMercyFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace" remark="next">你的人生不过是一出没有配角的《麦克白》；</speak>
            <remark post="U2FsdGVkX18BqSCxNHLELV1rn82a">
                <p class="article-text-h">注：</p>
                <p class="article-text">“卡莲”所说的每句带引号台词，都是莎士比亚名作《麦克白》里的成句。</p>
            </remark>
            <show chara="kallenChristSilentFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">“你的灵魂要是找得到天堂的话，那天晚上你早就该找到了。”</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">……</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">…………</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">我终于明白了。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">你什么都不懂——</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">——因为你也只是奥托·阿波卡利斯自己罢了。</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristDeterminedFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">……我当然不懂你。</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristMemoryFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">“最光明的天使也许会堕落，可是天使总是光明的”；</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristMercyFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">从一开始，我们就不一样。</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristDeterminedFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">这么多年过去了，只有你……只有你还不能接受我的死。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">啊。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">没错，我不能接受。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">从一开始，我就是那个盼望着圣诞节的孩子。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">渴求着名为卡莲·卡斯兰娜的礼物……</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">……不，是渴求着名为卡莲·卡斯兰娜的——圣诞老人。</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristMercyFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">……是啊，傻孩子。</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristDeterminedFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">在这件事上，你究竟要连累多少人才肯罢休？</speak>
            <bgm src="8_24_war.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">……</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">你错了。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">这和连累多少人根本没有关系。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">就像没有观测者的宇宙，永远也不会诞生赞美它的诗篇；</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">没有卡莲的世界，也不可能拥有存在的意义！</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristMercyFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">……太可怜了。</speak>
            <show chara="kallenChristDeterminedFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="kallenNoNameNoFace">你如今，只不过是个彻头彻尾的单相思变态而已。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">那又怎么样！</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">既然世界只留给了我一条路，那就不要怪我会清除掉所有的障碍物！</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">即使是我自己……</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">……即使是我自己，也不可能阻止这一切了！</speak>
            <goto goto="30" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="30" background="blackHole.jpg">
            <bgm src="8_24_war.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <text>“奥托”的外表已经无法维持人类的形态。</text>
            <text>在逐渐剥离的液态金属表皮之下，硬质的机械架构开始显露出来。</text>
            <text>瓦尔特咬紧牙关，仿佛要把全身的力量都灌输到“伊甸之星”当中。</text>
            <text>再努力一点。</text>
            <text>再努力一点，自己就可以为这纷乱的一天画上暂时的休止符。</text>
            <text>再努力一点，也许蕾安娜就能脱离那个人的控制。</text>
            <text>再努力一点——</text>
            <goto goto="40" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="40" background="black">
            <bgm src="8_24_war.mp3" status="stop"></bgm>
            <speak chara="ritaFullNameNoFace">瓦尔特，当心！</speak>
            <goto goto="50" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="50" background="CG26-2.jpg">
            <bgm src="8_24_war.mp3" status="stop"></bgm>
            <sound src="05_18_smash.mp3"/>
            <cg src="CG26-2.jpg" bg="CG26-2.jpg" fadeIn="0" fadeOut="1"></cg>
            <goto goto="60" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="60" background="blackCloud.jpg">
            <bgm src="11_17_tatakau.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <show chara="ottoLaughChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">制造黑洞……多么野蛮的能力啊。</speak>
            <show chara="ottoHaughtyChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">一旦坠入其中，那就真的连光线都无法逃脱了。</speak>
            <show chara="ottoConfidentChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">但反过来——只要还没跨过那不可逾越的界限，逃逸的速度就不会超过光速。</speak>
            <goto goto="70" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="70" background="CG26-3-1.jpg">
            <bgm src="11_17_tatakau.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">……是你大意了，律者。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">你什么时候产生了神之键就不会损坏的错觉呢？</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">这拟似的“约束之键”经过我的定向强化，可以完全封印攻击对象的崩坏能。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">现在，你不过就是一个手无缚鸡之力的匹夫罢了。</speak>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">……</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">思考也没有用，我可怜的朋友。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">你已经失去了制裁我的最好机会。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">胜券在握时便放松警惕，完全没有注意到那个状态下的神之键毫无防御力可言……</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">这是战斗经验的差距——</speak>
            <goto goto="80" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="80" background="CG26-3-2.jpg">
            <bgm src="11_17_tatakau.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">——你一个临阵磨枪的家伙，就少给我得意忘形了！</speak>
            <goto goto="90" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="90" background="blackCloud.jpg">
            <bgm src="horror.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">只需要一瞬间，</p>
                <br />
                <p class="article-text">天命的主教便能够反转所有人的命运。</p>
            </text>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">自己是手。</p>
                <p class="article-text">玛格丽塔是脚。</p>
                <p class="article-text">伤痕累累、毫无知觉的爱因斯坦和特斯拉，更是从头到脚被捆了个结结实实。</p>
            </text>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">所有的人，都被这可恶的锁链拘束了起来。</p>
                <br />
                <p class="article-text">无力挣脱，更无力反抗。</p>
            </text>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">等等……那是什么？</p>
                <br />
                <p class="article-text">……直升机？坠毁了？</p>
            </text>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">又抓来了几个不省人事的受害者吗——</p>
            </text>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">普朗克教授？</p>
                <br />
                <p class="article-text">约阿希姆？？</p>
            </text>
            <text article="1">
                <p class="article-text">怎么回事？？？</p>
                <br />
                <p class="article-text">你们为什么会出现在这里？！</p>
            </text>
            <goto goto="100" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="100" background="blackCloud.jpg">
            <bgm src="horror.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="ottoLaughChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">我记得东方有一句谚语说，“踏破铁鞋无觅处，得来全不费工夫。”</speak>
            <show chara="ottoScornfulChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">既然有人如此飞蛾扑火——那么不分次序一并处决，反而是我的不对了。</speak>
            <show chara="ottoConfidentChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">一个一个来怎么样？</speak>
            <show chara="ottoHaughtyChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">当然，瓦尔特要留到最后。</speak>
            <show chara="ottoConfidentChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">六个人，六条锁链，六种死相……</speak>
            <show chara="ottoLaughChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">……就从小朋友你开始吧？</speak>
            <goto goto="110" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="110" background="bloodWhite.jpg">
            <bgm src="horror.mp3" status="stop"></bgm>
            <sound src="05_18_claw.mp3"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">……嗯？</speak>
            <goto goto="120" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="120" background="blackCloud.jpg">
            <bgm src="horror.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <show chara="ottoHaughtyChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">啧，竟然拼尽全力，也要给孩子挡枪吗？</speak>
            <show chara="ottoScornfulChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">扫兴。</speak>
            <show chara="ottoHaughtyChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">不过看在你盛情难却的份上，在下就换一个人开始吧。</speak>
            <show chara="ottoScornfulChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">……</speak>
            <show chara="ottoHaughtyChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">老板娘，你还有什么大言不惭的话要说吗？</speak>
            <speak chara="ritaFullNameNoFace">……</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">……声音太小我听不见啊？</speak>
            <show chara="ottoScornfulChainFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">——到面前来说吧！</speak>
            <goto goto="125" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="125" background="black">
            <bgm src="horror.mp3" status="stop"></bgm>
            <speak chara="ritaFullNameNoFace">（哼。）</speak>
            <goto goto="130" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="130" background="CG26-4-2.jpg">
            <bgm src="11_17_tatakau.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <cg src="CG26-4-1.jpg" bg="CG26-4-2.jpg" fadeIn="0" fadeOut="1"></cg>
            <speak chara="ritaFullNameNoFace">得意忘形的人是你！奥托！</speak>
            <goto goto="140" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="140" background="errorBlack.jpg">
            <bgm src="11_17_tatakau.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">（这、这是怎么回事！）</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">（发生了什么？信号中断了？）</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">（不……不对……）</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFace">（魂钢皮肤……发生了紊乱？）</speak>
            <bgm src="04_20_Brigantia.mp3" status="start"></bgm>
            <speak chara="ritaFullNameNoFace">瓦尔特！快上！</speak>
            <speak chara="ritaFullNameNoFace">还记得你一直揣在兜里的防狼喷雾吗？</speak>
            <speak chara="ritaFullNameNoFace">那是魂钢抑制剂！他的液态皮肤被临时固化了！</speak>
            <speak chara="ritaFullNameNoFace">帮我砸开这堆破铜烂铁！</speak>
            <goto goto="150" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="150" background="nebula.jpg">
            <bgm src="04_20_Brigantia.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="weltNakedNormalFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">……伤口临时止血——完毕。</speak>
            <show chara="weltNakedCoatNormalFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">……进入本体拟态模式。</speak>
            <show chara="weltNakedCoatShoutFar" position="center"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">我的双拳啊，化作真正的“犹大誓约”吧！</speak>
            <goto goto="160" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="160" background="CG26-5.jpg">
            <bgm src="04_20_Brigantia.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <sound src="05_18_smash.mp3"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">给我滚出蕾安娜的身体！你这个跳梁小丑！！</speak>
            <goto goto="170" change="#ffffff"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="170" background="CG26-6-1.jpg">
            <bgm src="04_20_Brigantia.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFaceRed">（……哼。愚蠢。）</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFaceRed">（只不过是个临时身体而已——）</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFaceRed">（——就算是与你们同归于尽，那又如何？）</speak>
            <goto goto="180" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="180" background="errorWhite.jpg">
            <bgm src="04_20_Brigantia.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFaceGreen">……？</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFaceGreen">（怎么回事？）</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFaceGreen">（连自爆程序也不能工作了吗？）</speak>
            <speak chara="reannaNoNameNoFace">……你可真是干了件了不起的事情啊，我的奥托大人。</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFaceGreen">不……不可能……</speak>
            <speak chara="ottoNoFaceGreen">你……你是……</speak>
            <goto goto="190" change="0"/>
        </scene>
        <scene id="190" background="CG26-6-2.jpg">
            <bgm src="04_20_Brigantia.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <speak chara="reannaNoNameNoFace">怎么？直到刚才还在用人家的身体耀武扬威，却竟然不记得这个声音了吗？</speak>
            <speak chara="reannaNoNameNoFace">……话说，在当初第一次用“虚空万藏”改造我身体的时候，你就想好了今天的这一出吧？</speak>
            <speak chara="reannaNoNameNoFace">……整整一百年的“忒修斯之船”。</speak>
            <speak chara="reannaNoNameNoFace">奥托大人，你可真有耐心。</speak>
            <speak chara="reannaNoNameNoFace">不过……你知道吗？</speak>
