        <scene id="240" background="blackCloud.jpg">
            <bgm src="04_20_tank.mp3" status="continue"></bgm>
            <show chara="ritaNervousHeadphoneGunClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="ritaFullNameNoFace">这是……洲际导弹？</speak>
            <speak chara="ritaFullNameNoFace">动能估计值有这么大吗？</speak>
            <show chara="ritaNervousHeadphoneGunClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="reaChangeSeriousClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="reannaNoFace">不……比那个更糟。</speak>
            <speak chara="reannaNoFace">……这几年里，受柏林崩坏事件的启发，总部秘密开发了一种能够在瞬时再现崩坏爆发的炸弹——</speak>
            <speak chara="reannaNoFace">——崩坏裂变弹。</speak>
            <show chara="reaChangeSeriousClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltNakedCoatSurpriseClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">那是……什么？</speak>
            <show chara="weltNakedCoatSurpriseClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="reaChangeSeriousClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="reannaNoFace">……崩坏裂变弹通过物理上的连锁反应，人为将虚数侧的大量崩坏能在极短时间内聚合并释放，从而达到毁灭周遭一切物质的效果。</speak>
            <speak chara="reannaNoFace">正因为如此，这种武器，被它的开发者们视为对抗律者和崩坏兽的终极底牌。</speak>
            <show chara="reaChangeSeriousClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltNakedCoatSurpriseClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">一旦在这里爆炸的话——</speak>
            <show chara="weltNakedCoatSurpriseClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="reaChangeSeriousClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="reannaNoFace">……不仅我们所有人将自身难保；爱迪生小姐为了保护这座城市所做的全部努力，也会变得毫无意义。</speak>
            <show chara="reaChangeSeriousClose" position="right" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="weltNakedCoatSurpriseClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">……</speak>
            <show chara="weltNakedCoatShoutClose" position="left"/>
            <speak chara="weltNoFace">这太荒谬了！</speak>
            <show chara="weltNakedCoatShoutClose" position="left" opacity="0.7"/>
            <show chara="reaChangeSeriousClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="reannaNoFace">……</speak>
            <show chara="reaChangeConfidentClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="reannaNoFace">别慌。</speak>
            <speak chara="reannaNoFace">我们至少还有一个对抗的手段。</speak>
            <show chara="reaChangeNormalClose" position="right"/>
            <speak chara="reannaNoFace">为了所有人的希望……瓦尔特，请你配合好我接下来的行动。</speak>
